  "title": "Human Resource (HR) Executive / Associate HR Consultant",
  "description": "<h3>💼 Now Hiring: Associate HR Consultant & Customer Service<br /></h3><p>We’re looking for a <strong>driven individual</strong> to join our dynamic team. This role offers a unique opportunity to work across diverse industries, engage with a wide range of stakeholders, and contribute to impactful HR and business consulting projects.</p><p>🌟 What You’ll Do:</p><ul><li>Create consultancy deliverables: reports, presentations, training materials</li><li>Assist in HR and business consultancy projects</li><li>Help organize and deliver client training programs</li><li>Translate documents between English and Chinese</li><li>Communicate effectively with internal and external stakeholders</li><li>Provide HR operations, payroll, and recruitment services to retainer clients</li><li>Contribute to marketing and sales initiatives</li><li>Follow up with new customers</li><li>You are required to work after office hours sometimes</li></ul><p>✅ What We’re Looking For:</p><ul><li>Strong communication and time management skills</li><li>Proactive, accountable, and eager to learn</li><li>Able to communicate with English-speaking and Chinese-speaking customers</li></ul><p>🎁 What You’ll Get:</p><ul><li>Broad exposure to multiple industries and clients</li><li>Competitive base salary + profit-sharing scheme</li><li>A collaborative, growth-focused work environment</li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please email your UPDATED CV to jiayi@careerstar.com.sg.<br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br /></p><p>Careerstar International Pte Ltd.</p><p>EA License No: 03C3254</p><p>EA Personnel No: R23112939</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Loh Jia Yi</p>",
